---

# Failure Conditions

Reject a hypothesis if:

It cannot be tested.

It cannot be measured.

It changes multiple strategic variables.

It has no commercial value.

It produces no learning.

It has no success criteria.

---

# Success Criteria

A successful hypothesis engine allows Creative Strategist AI to answer:

What are we trying to prove?

Why does this deserve budget?

What will we learn?

What should happen if we are right?

What should happen if we are wrong?

Which hypothesis deserves testing first?

Only then can creative production begin.
